- The integer array parameter `nums` must not be null.
- The integer array parameter `removeQueries` must not be null.
- The length of the integer array parameter `nums` is equal to the length of the integer array parameter `removeQueries`.
- The integer array result `answer` must not be null.
- The length of the integer array result `answer` is equal to the length of the integer array parameter `nums`.
- Each element in the integer array result `answer` is the maximum segment sum after applying the corresponding removal query.
- The maximum segment sum is the sum of every element in a segment of contiguous positive integers in the `nums` array after applying the removal query.